translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,170,"Xa kusithiwa kubo: “Landelani oko uAllâh Akutyhilileyo”. Bathi bona: “Nakanye! Thina silandela oko sakubona kulandelwa ngoobawo bethu”. Nangona oobawo babo babengaqiqi bengekho naphantsi kwesiKhokelo"
  2,171,"Umzekelo wabo bangakholwayo unje ngomntu okhwaza umhlambi wezimvu ongavi nento le ngaphandle kwenkwaza nezikhalo. Bazizithulu, izimumu neemfama. Abaqiqi"
  2,172,"Hini na nina bakholwayo yityani izinto ezivumelekileyo eSininike zona, nibe nombulelo kuAllâh, Ukuba ngaba ngenene nguYe eniMnqulayo"
  2,173,"Yena Unalele ukuba (nitye) isilwanyana esizifeleyo, igazi, nenyama yehagu, nento exhelelwe ukwenziwa idini kwenye into engengoAllâh. Kodwa ukuba ubani uthe wanyanzeliswa engazithandelanga, engaqhutywa lugabadelo, kulowo akukho sono. Inene uAllâh nguMxoleli Onenceba"
  2,174,"Inene abo bafihla oko uAllâh Akutyhilileyo kuseNcwadini, bathenge inzuzwana encinane ngako oko. Abatyi nto yimbi eziswini zabo ngaphandle koMlilo, uAllâh Akayi kuthetha nokuthetha nabo ngoMhla woVuko, Engayi kubahlambulula, yaye okwabo iya kuba sisohlwayo esibuhlungu"
  2,175,"Abo ngabo bathenga ukulahleka ngexabiso lesiKhokelo, nesohlwayo ngexabiso lokuxolelwa. Hayi ukuzithemba abanako ngokubhekiselele eMlilweni"
  2,176,Oko kungenxa yokuba uAllâh Uthumele iNcwadi (i’Kur`ân) ngenyaniso. Inene Abo baphikayo ngokumayela neNcwadi (baphambuke) bakude lee ngokuphikisa (kwabo)